Package Description
pp2016.team19.client
Contains the ClientMain to start the ClientEngine
pp2016.team19.client.comm
Comprises the communication classes for the client-side which are necessary to set up a proper communication between client and server.
pp2016.team19.client.engine
Contains the ClientEngine class.
pp2016.team19.client.gui
Contains the classes for the GUI.
pp2016.team19.server
Contains the ServMain to start the ServerEngine.
pp2016.team19.server.comm
Comprises the communication classes for the server-side which are necessary to set up a proper communication between server and client.
pp2016.team19.server.engine
Comprises the classes being responsible for the management of the game.
pp2016.team19.server.map
Contains a test class to test the levelgenerator.
pp2016.team19.shared
Contains all shared classes.
